Template: mirror/suite
Type: select
Choices-C: ${CHOICES-C}
Choices: ${CHOICES}
# :sl2:
_Description: Parrot version to install:
 Parrot comes in several flavors.
 .
 Parrot LTS
 LTS is the Long Term Support distribution where software is slower to update but more reliable.
 It also receives fast security updates.
 .
 Parrot Rolling
 Rolling is a version of parrot that receives continuos updates and the software is always available
 at its latest version.
 The system is less reliable but it offers a perfect environment for developers and testers (or arch users).


